<description>
Provides the location of the local Niagara Home directory.&#xa;&#xa; Note, do not use this method to construct the location of system subdirectories, such as the&#xa; &lt;code&gt;modules&lt;/code&gt; directory, which have their own utility methods in this class&#xa; (see &lt;code&gt;<see ref="javax.baja.nre.util.SystemFiles#getModulesDirectory()">#getModulesDirectory()</see>&lt;/code&gt;).
</description>
<return>
<type class="java.io.File"/>
<description>
the location of the local Niagara Home directory
</description>
</return>
